                  </hi>. I am a gardener, and live in England-lane, Hampstead. I missed from my garden a dung-fork, a kettle, a piece of flannel, and a gimlet—these are the articles—I can swear to them—I missed them on Tuesday morning—the pales were pulled down to get into the garden.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. I throw myself on the mercy of the Court.</p>
